PA_SLA_CRITERIA.NAME: Quality of Delivery
PA_SLA_CRITERIA.DESCRIPTION: Rate the quality of delivery from 1=best to 6=worst

PA_SLA_CRITERIA.NAME: Delivery Accuracy
PA_SLA_CRITERIA.DESCRIPTION: How accurate is the promise date?
PA_SLA_CRITERIA.HELP: The measure are the average days between promise date (PO/SO) and delivery date (Material receipt/shipment) It is positive if before, negative if later. The lower the number, the better
